  "notes": [
    "This clinical practice guideline provides recommendations for diagnosing Cushing's syndrome using various biochemical tests and procedures.",
    "The guideline emphasizes a stepwise approach with initial screening tests followed by confirmatory testing.",
    "Special consideration is given to cyclic hypercortisolism and patients with adrenal incidentalomas."
